name: Imageclick
body: ### Welcome to ImageClick This is a software for revealing Images panel after panel developed by @nicolaiimmanuelschmid. This could become a compatitive game for guessing whats the actual motive of the Image. ### OpenBETA The software is now in openBETA and I'm hoping to get a few bug reports. ###Download You can download the software itself as well as the sourcecode here on GitHub. ###Contribution I am open for contributors, if anyone is interested.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
